  <body>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p>Welcome to <%= title %>!</p>
    <p>Adam is running the <a href="http://www.leicestermarathon.org.uk/">Leicester half marathon</a> on Sunday 26th of October 2014 to raise funds for the Leicester Hospice - <a href="http://www.loros.co.uk/">LOROS</a></p>
    <p>LOROS provide care and support to terminally ill adult patients and their family.</p>
    <h2>So what's this all about?</h2>
    <p>On <b>Monday 20th of October 2014</b> Adam will be making coffee/tea runs to Starbucks between <b>10am-4pm</b>, order your drink below and get it delivered right to your office/room within the CS building.</p>
    <p>A minimum 50p charity surcharge will be added to the stanard cost of the drink (rounded up to the nearest 50p for cash orders). You can also pay with PayPal.</p>

